        <td style="padding: 20px; color: #333;">
          <p>Hi <strong>{{email}}</strong>,</p>
          <p>Thank you for registering with us. Please use the following One-Time Code to verify your email address:</p>
          <div style="text-align: center; margin: 25px 0;">
            <span style="font-size: 28px; font-weight: bold; letter-spacing: 8px; color: #4CAF50;">
              {{otp}}
            </span>
          </div>
          <p>This code is valid for <strong>10 minutes</strong>. If you did not create this account, please ignore this email.</p>
